Package: cpDNABarcoder
Type: Package
Title: Extraction and Analysis of Chloroplast DNA Barcode Markers
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Pheris",
    family = "Namakwa",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "pherisn@gmail.com"
    )
Description: Provides tools for extracting, validating, quality-controlling,
    exporting, and summarizing chloroplast DNA barcode markers from GenBank
    genome records. The package supports standard plant DNA barcodes such as
    rbcL, matK, and psbA-trnH, together with reporting and batch-processing
    workflows.
